          "%md",
          "",
          "# Financial Crime Investigation Graph, RDF, and AI Agents",
          "",
          "This merged notebook combines the property graph account-analysis notebook with the RDF Graph + AI Agents notebook.",
          "",
          "The chronological story is:",
          "",
          "1. Build the relational investigation data.",
          "2. Create the property graph and prove the network evidence.",
          "3. Add Select AI over the property graph.",
          "4. Create the RDF graph and prove OWL2RL inference.",
          "5. Expose RDF evidence through PL/SQL functions and AI agent tools.",
          "6. Ask natural-language questions that connect the property graph and RDF evidence."
        ],
