          "",
          "- Oracle AI Database 26ai or Autonomous AI Database 26ai.",
          "- A schema such as FINANCIAL_DEMO with privileges to create tables, views, PL/SQL functions, and property graphs.",
          "- RDF Graph enabled, with an RDF network named RDF_NETWORK owned by FINANCIAL_DEMO or adjusted in the SQL.",
