        "title": "Q1 context",
        "hasTitle": false,
        "message": [
          "%md",
          "**Q1: Customer-first with reverse lookup**",
          "",
          "The analyst only knows a customer id. No case id. Watch the agent:",
          "1. Call the entity tool with C300",
          "2. Return the inferred risk classifications",
          "3. Find CASE-1042 via reverse lookup — without being told the case id",
          "",
          "This is the key moment: the analyst asked about a customer, the agent found the case."
        ],
        "selectedVisualization": null,
        "visualizationConfig": null,
        "hideCode": false,
        "hideResult": false,
        "hideGutter": true,
        "hideVizConfig": false,
        "hideInIFrame": false,
