        "hasTitle": false,
        "message": [
          "%md",
          "# What just happened",
          "",
          "**The property graph** found A300 because it shares a device with a flagged account. Structural signal.",
          "",
          "**The RDF graph** flagged A300 because its owner lives in a sanctioned jurisdiction. Semantic signal.",
          "",
          "Neither system knew about the other. The same account appeared in both.",
          "",
          "---",
          "",
          "**Select AI** gives natural language over SQL and property graph.",
          "",
          "**Agents** give the same thing over RDF — and because OWL2RL is running underneath, the answers include conclusions that were **never explicitly stored in the data**.",
          "",
          "We didn't program C300 to be high risk. We told the system where C300 lives. The ontology did the rest."
        ],
